demo.name: HackGT 12
demo.description:
HackGT is HexLabs' annual 36-hour hackathon taking place at Georgia Tech. From September 26th to September 28th, the event will welcome over 1500 hackers from around the world to engage in innovative challenges, networking opportunities, and win exciting prizes. The event is open to all skill levels and includes various tracks, a sponsor fair, and mini-events.

 Links: https://hack.gt/
